<http://www.spektrix.com/capilanouniversity/event/17802ARQGCSKTDGDBPGBHPTGHVHPJJQMJ>
  a schema:Event;
  schema:name "The Importance of Being Earnest";
  schema:description """
	<h2><span class=\"ItalicText\"><span class=\"BoldText\">The Importance of Being Earnest</span></span></h2>by Oscar Wilde<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Two dashing young men, Jack and Algernon, discover that they both have been using secret identities to let loose away from their family obligations. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>But when they find that their double-lives come with a double-edged sword, Jack and Algernon must untangle a web of deceit to win the hearts of the women they love.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Often considered Oscar Wilde’s masterpiece, <span class=\"ItalicText\">The Importance of Being Earnest</span> sparkles with wit, love, absurdity and laughter.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Directed by Chllton Crane<span><br/></span><span><br/></span><h2><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.caputheatre.com/\">CapU Theatre Website</a></h2><span><br/></span>Relaxed Performance: Saturday November 21<span><br/></span><a target=\"_blank\" href=\"https://www.capilanou.ca/media/capilanouca/student-life/capu-community/blueshore-financial-centre-for-performing-arts/documents/Visual-Story.pdf\">Visual Story for the Theatre</a><span><br/></span>
""";
